; PocketCrawl master Theme.
; PD layout (sharp 2-3px corners, banner-style headers, mobile tap targets)
; with DCSS CGA-16 monochrome palette (near-black bg, LightGray borders/text,
; Yellow hover, LightCyan accent). Galmuri11 pixel font as default.
;
; Single source of truth — GameTheme.create() loads this.
; Layout token constants (TYPO_*, PAD_*, TAP_MIN_HEIGHT) live in GameTheme.gd.

[gd_resource type="Theme" load_steps=20 format=3 uid="uid://b_pcr_theme_002"]

[ext_resource type="FontFile" path="res://assets/fonts/Galmuri11.ttf" id="1_font"]

